<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٦٩٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6106">مُسْلِمُ بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6685">هِشَامٌ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">وَشُعْبَةُ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> رَأَى رَجُلًا يَسُوقُ بَدَنَةً،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> ارْكَبْهَا،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> إِنَّهَا بَدَنَةٌ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ارْكَبْهَا،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> إِنَّهَا بَدَنَةٌ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ارْكَبْهَا. ثَلَاثًا»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>